/* positioning is the same on all viewports */

.prev-next {
	height: 0;
	position: static;
	width: 0;
}

.prev-next .prev,
.prev-next .next {
	height: 5.4rem;
	left: 50%;
	top: 28.7rem; /* height of headers, also controlled by .subnav-exists in thecut context. */
	width: 4.4rem;
	z-index: 102; /* needs to go above elements on page, but below a popup ad */
}

.prev-next .prev {
	margin-left: -58.4rem;
}

.prev-next .next {
	margin-left: 54rem;
}

/* initial state */

.prev-next a {
	background-color: #f9f9f9;
	background-position: center 2.1rem;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: 0 0;
	border: 1px solid #dbdbdb;
	border-radius: .5rem;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	height: 100%;
	left: 0;
	line-height: 1.2;
	overflow: hidden;
	padding: .6rem;
	position: absolute;
	text-align: left;
	text-decoration: none;
	top: 0;
	transition: border 250ms ease-out, background-color 250ms ease-out, opacity .3s;
	width: 100%;
}

.prev-next a .link-text {
	display: inline-block;
	opacity: 0;
	padding-top: .5rem;
}

.prev-next a.on {
	background-color: #dbdbdb;
	border: 1px solid #bcbcbc;
	transition: border 130ms linear, background-color 130ms linear;
}

.prev-next .prev a {
	left: 0;
	right: auto;
}

.prev-next a.empty {
	display: none;
}

/* arrows */

.prev-next .prev-arrow,
.prev-next .next-arrow {
	height: 60%;
	left: 20%;
	position: absolute;
	top: 20%;
	width: 60%;
}

.prev-next .prev-arrow svg,
.prev-next .next-arrow svg {
	fill: #7d7d7d !important;
	height: 100%;
	left: 50%;
	margin-left: -9px;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	width: 16px;
}

.prev-next .next-arrow {
	-webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);
	        transform: rotate(180deg);
}

}

/* Vertical */

.img.primary.vertical-small {
	float: left;
	left: -2rem;
	margin: .5rem 0 1rem;
	max-width: 13.7rem;
}

.img.primary.vertical-small figcaption {
	padding: .4rem 0 0 2rem;
}

/* Large Vertical */

.img.primary.vertical {
	left: -2rem;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
	width: calc(100% + 4rem);
}

/* Horizontal */

.img.primary.horizontal {
	clear: both;
	left: -2rem;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
	width: calc(100% + 4rem);
}

/* Enlarge */

.img .enlarge {
	background-color: rgba(255,255,255, .85);
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	border-radius: .3rem;
	display: none;
	float: right;
	height: 3.4rem;
	line-height: 0;
	margin: 0 0 .6rem 1rem;
	padding: .4rem;
	text-align: center;
	width: 3.4rem;
}

.img .enlarge svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	left: .1rem;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.8rem;
}

/* Enlarged Image */

.img.enlarged {
	display: block;
	height: 100%;
	left: 0;
	top: 0;
	margin: 0 auto;
	max-width: none;
	position: absolute;
	text-align: center;
	width: 100%;
	z-index: 1001;
}

.img.enlarged aside {
	bottom: .5rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: .5rem;
}

.img.enlarged .enlarge {
	display: none;
}

.img.enlarged .close {
	background: none;
	border: 1px solid #3b3b3b;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: block;
	height: 3.6rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: .5rem;
	top: .5rem;
	transition: border-color .25s ease-in;
	width: 3.6rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg {
	height: 1.6rem;
	left: 0;
	margin: .9rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.6rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg path {
	fill: #fff;
}

/* Pinterest and facebook*/

.img aside a.fb,
.img aside a.pinterest {
	display: block;
	float: right;
	line-height: 0;
	padding: .3rem 1rem;
}

.img aside a.fb {
	padding-right: .2rem;
}

.body > .img.primary aside a.fb,
.body > .img.primary aside a.pinterest {
	display: none;
}

.img.enlarged aside a.fb,
.img.enlarged aside a.pinterest {
	opacity: 1;
}

.img aside a.fb svg,
.img aside a.pinterest svg {
	height: 2.5rem;
	width: 2.5rem;
}

/* Slideshow button on top of primary image. */

.img.slideshow-link > div > a {
	bottom: 0;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	top: 0;
	z-index: 10;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a button {
	background-color: #000;
	border: 0;
	bottom: 1.5rem;
	color: #fff;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.3rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	letter-spacing: .1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	left: .8rem;
	padding: .5rem 1rem 1.2rem 1.5rem;
	position: absolute;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	transition: background-color 0.2s;
	-webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a svg {
	display: inline-block;
	height: 2rem;
	margin: 0 .5rem 0;
	position: relative;
	top: .5rem;
	width: 2rem;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for large vertical on mobile. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical > div > img {
	margin-top: 4rem;
}

.img.slideshow-link.vertical > div > a button {
	bottom: auto;
	left: 0;
	letter-spacing: 0;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .5rem 1rem 1.2rem .7rem;
	top: 0;
	width: 100%;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for vertical-small on mobile. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical-small > div > a button {
	bottom: 0;
	left: 0;
	letter-spacing: 0;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 1.1rem 1rem 1rem .7rem;
	width: 100%;
}

.img.slideshow-link.vertical-small > div > a svg {
	display: none;
}

.related-side {

.related-side h2,
.story .body .related-side h2 {

	font-size: 1.3rem;

}

.related-side a,
.story .body .related-side a {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;

/* container */

.share {
	background: transparent;
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	display: block;
	height: 3.7rem;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	position: relative;
}

.share.vertical {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	display: block;
}

.share.horizontal {
	height: 3.5rem;
}

/* title */

.share .share-text {
	color: #555;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.3rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 1.1rem 0 0 3rem;
	z-index: -2;
}

.share.overlay.on .share-text {
	display: none;
}

/* total share count */

.share .share-counter {
	display: none;
}

/* share link */

.share a {
	color: transparent;
	display: block;
	float: left;
	height: 3.3rem;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .7rem .3rem .6rem .3rem;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	width: 2.7rem;
	z-index: -1;
}

/* Icons */

.share a:first-of-type {
	margin-left: .5rem;
}

.share a svg {
	height: 2rem;
	width: 2rem;
}

.share a.email {
	border: 1px solid #ddd;
	border-radius: .3rem;
	height: 2.2rem;
	margin: .6rem .8rem 0 .3rem;
	padding: .5rem .4rem;
	width: 2.2rem;
}

.share a.email svg {
	height: 1.2rem;
	width: 1.2rem;
}

/* Stuff to hide. */

.share a em {
	display: none;
}

.share .comments {
	display: none;
}

.share .print {
	display: none;
}

.share .close {
	display: none;
}

/* overlay wrapper */

.share-overlay-wrapper {
	-webkit-align-items: center;
	    -ms-flex-align: center;
	        align-items: center;
	display: -webkit-flex;
	display: -ms-flexbox;
	display: flex;
	height: 100%;
	-webkit-justify-content: center;
	    -ms-flex-pack: center;
	        justify-content: center;
	left: 0;
	position: fixed;
	top: 0;
	width: 100%;
	z-index: -100;
}

.share-overlay-wrapper.on {
	z-index: 900000;
}

/* overlay clone */

.share.overlay {
	background: #f9f9f7;
	border: 1px solid #ddd;
	border-radius: .25rem;
	box-shadow: .1rem .1rem .4rem #ccc;
	display: block;
	height: auto;
	opacity: 0;
	padding: 3.9rem 3rem 3rem;
	transition: opacity 50ms;
	width: 21.4rem;
	z-index: -100; /* allows for transition */
}

.share.overlay.on {
	opacity: 1;
	z-index: 900000; /* above all other content */
	transition: opacity 300ms;
}

.share.overlay::before {
	background: inherit;
	bottom: auto;
	color: #000;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 3rem;
	padding: 0;
	position: absolute;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	top: 1.5rem;
	z-index: auto;
}

/* overlay: share link */

.share.overlay a {
	background-color: #fff;
	background-position: .8rem .6rem;
	background-size: 2.1rem 2.1rem;
	border: 1px solid #dadada;
	border-radius: .2rem;
	bottom: auto;
	color: #555;
	float: none;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
	height: 3.4rem;
	margin: 0 auto 1.6rem;
	padding: .8rem 0 0 3.7rem;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	top: auto;
	width: 15rem;
	z-index: auto;
}

.share.overlay svg {
	left: .8rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: .6rem;
}

.share.overlay .email svg {
	height: 2rem;
	left: .8rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: .8rem;
	width: 2rem;
}

.share.overlay .print {
	display: block;
}

.share.overlay .print svg {
	height: 2.7rem;
	left: .5rem;
	top: .3rem;
	width: 2.7rem;
}

/* overlay: count */

.share.overlay a em {
	border-left: 1px solid #dadada;
	bottom: 0;
	color: #000;
	display: block;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: bold;
	padding: .8rem 0 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	text-align: center;
	top: 0;
	width: 5.1rem;
}

/* overlay: specific share tools */

.share.overlay .close {
	background: none;
	border: 0;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: block;
	height: 3.2rem;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	top: 0;
	width: 3.2rem;
}

.share.overlay .close svg {
	height: 2.8rem;
	left: .2rem;
	top: .2rem;
	width: 2.8rem;
}

/* hide whatsapp (except on ios) */

.share .whatsapp {
	display: none;
}

.share .whatsapp.displayed {
	display: block;
}

.share-feed.no-count,
.newsfeed .share-feed {
	display: none;
}

.share-feed  div.share-count,
.greatest-hits .share-feed div.share-count,
.most-popular .share-feed div.share-count,
.newsfeed .share-feed div.share-count,
.top-stories .share-feed div.share-count {
	color: #f85d00;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: bold;
	height: auto;
	line-height: 1;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
}

.share-feed  div.share-count em,
.greatest-hits .share-feed div.share-count em,
.most-popular .share-feed div.share-count em,
.newsfeed .share-feed div.share-count em {
	color: #555;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
}

.share-feed  a,
.greatest-hits .share-feed  a,
.most-popular .share-feed  a,
.newsfeed .share-feed  a {
	display: none;
}

/* Article Header */

.story {
	clear: both;
	padding-bottom: 2rem;
	position: relative;
	word-wrap: break-word;
}

.story header {
	margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.story header nav {
	clear: both;
	display: block;
	margin: 0 0 1rem;
	height: 3.8rem;
	padding: 0;
}

.story.sponsored header nav {
	padding: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.story header nav .rubric {
	min-height: 2.5rem;
	padding-top: 2px;
	white-space: nowrap;
}

.story header nav a {
	color: #111;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	height: 2rem;
	line-height: 2.5rem;
	text-decoration: none;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.story header nav a:first-child {
	display: block;
	float: left;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-weight: normal;
	margin-right: .5rem;
	padding-right: 1.3rem;
	text-transform: capitalize;
	white-space: nowrap;
}

.story header nav a:first-child::after {
	color: #999;
	content: '/';
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	left: .9rem;
	position: relative;
	top: .2rem;
}

.story header nav a:last-child::after {
	content: '';
}

.story header nav span.exclusive {
	color: #00bcf1;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	text-transform: capitalize;
}

.story header nav span.breaking {
	color: #ec2c00;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	text-transform: capitalize;
}

.story.sponsored header nav span.sponsored-tag,
.story.sponsored header nav span.sponsored-tag:last-child {
	background-color: #ff003d;
	border-radius: .2rem;
	color: #fff;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	padding: .6rem 1rem;
	position: relative;
	text-transform: none;
	top: 1rem;
}

.story header h1 {
	font-family: GeorgiaProCondSemiBold, serif;
	font-size: 2.4rem;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 2.4rem;
	margin: 0 0 1rem;
}

.story.sponsored header h1 {
	color: #323232;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: bold;
}

.story header p {
	color: #333;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	line-height: 1.3rem;
}

/* Byline */

.story header .by-authors {
	color: #333;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
	margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
	width: 90%;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author {
	color: #333;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 0;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	transition: color .25s;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author:first-child {
	padding-left: 0;
}

.story header .by-authors iframe {
	margin-left: 1rem;
	position: relative;
	top: .4rem;
}

/* Author Avatar */

.story header .by-authors .story-author-img {
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: contain;
	border-radius: 4.5rem;
	display: inline-block;
	height: 4rem;
	margin: 0 .5rem 0 0;
	vertical-align: middle;
	width: 4rem;
}

/* Stacked format - img + name + twitter */

.story header .by-authors.stacked {
	margin-bottom: -0.4rem;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked,
.story header .by-authors.stacked .story-author {
	display: block;
	margin-top: 1.4rem;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .story-author-img {
	position: relative;
	top: -0.4rem;
	vertical-align: top;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .by {
	font-weight: normal;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author:hover .by {
	color: #000;
	cursor: text;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .twitter {
	left: 3rem;
	position: relative;
	top: -2rem;
}

/* Time */

.story header time {
	color: #999;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	padding: .6rem 0 1rem;
}

/* Article Body */

.story .body {
	color: #111;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	line-height: 2.2rem;
}

.story .body figure.story-img {
	left: -2rem;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
	width: calc(100% + 4rem);
}

.story .body figure.story-img figcaption {
	margin: 0 auto;
	width: 90%;
}

/* Slideshow button at the end of the article. */

.story .body a.begin-slideshow {
	background-color: #000;
	border: 1px solid #222;

}

.story .body .video-embed {

}

	width: 100%;
}

}

}

}

.story .body .fb-post {

}

.story .body .imgur-embed img {
	width: 100%;
}

.story .body h2 {
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	line-height: 2.2rem;
	margin: 3rem 0 1rem;
}

.story .body p {
	margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
}

.story .body a {
	color: #1782a9;
	padding: 0;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.story .body ul {
	clear: both;
	line-height: 2.3rem;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0 0 0 1rem;
}

.story .body ul li {
	list-style: none;
	margin: 0 0 2rem;
}

.story .body ul li:before {
	color: #999;
	content: '•';
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
}

.story .body ol {
	counter-reset: list;
	margin: 3rem 0;
	padding: 0 0 0 2rem;
}

.story .body ol li {
	display: block;
	list-style: none;
	margin: 0 0 2rem;
	padding: 0;
}

.story .body ol li:before {
	color: #999;
	content: counter(list);
	counter-increment: list;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
}

.story .body blockquote:before {
	border-top: 5px solid #e2e2e0;
	content: '';
	display: inline;
	margin-top: -1.4rem;
	position: absolute;
	width: 4.5rem;
}

.story .body blockquote,
.story .body blockquote p {
	color: #5a5a5a;

	line-height: 2.3rem;
	margin: 0 0 1.5rem;

.story .body blockquote p {

}

	padding: 0;

}

/* Article Footer */

.story footer cite a {
	background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/source.2x.png);

	background-size: .9rem .9rem;

	font-size: 1rem;
	font-style: normal;

.story .rooseSidebar {

/* primary image slideshow button (on mobile) */

.story .body a.begin-slideshow,

	color: #fff;

.story .img.vertical-small-variable.slideshow-link > div > a svg

.cut-nav .nav-mobile:before,
.cut-nav .nav-mobile:after {
	border-right: 1px solid #343434;
	content: '';
	height: 2.5rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 1.2rem;
	width: 1px;
}

.cut-nav .nav-mobile:before {
	left: .2rem;
}

.cut-nav .nav-mobile:after {
	right: .2rem;
}

.cut-nav .nav-mobile.on {
	background-color: #1a1a1a;
	border: 1px solid #4f4f4f;
	border-bottom: none;
	border-top-left-radius: 3px;
	border-top-right-radius: 3px;
	height: 6.1rem;
	z-index: 99999999;
}

.cut-nav .nav-mobile.on:before,
.cut-nav .nav-mobile.on:after {
	display: none;
}

.cut-nav .nav-mobile.on svg,
.cut-nav .nav-mobile.on svg * {
	fill: #fff !important;
}

/* Dropdown */

.cut-nav .dropdown {
	background-color: #1a1a1a;
	border-top: 1px solid #4f4f4f;
	display: none;
	padding: 2.3rem 0;
	position: absolute;
	top: 7.5rem;
	width: 100%;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown:after {
	clear: both;
	content: '';
	display: block;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown.on {
	-webkit-animation-duration: 250ms;
	        animation-duration: 250ms;
	-webkit-animation-fill-mode: forwards;
	        animation-fill-mode: forwards;
	-webkit-animation-name: DropdownOpen;
	        animation-name: DropdownOpen;
	-webkit-animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(.215,  .610, .355, 1.000);
	        animation-timing-function: cubic-bezier(.215,  .610, .355, 1.000); /* ease-out-cubic */
	display: block;
	z-index: 9999999;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section {
	border-left: 1px solid #272727;
	float: left;
	height: 26rem;
	padding: 0 2.3rem;
	width: 25%;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section:first-of-type {
	border: none;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section:before {
	color: #979797;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: bold;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section > h2,
.cut-nav .dropdown-section > a,
.cut-nav .dropdown-section > a:visited {
	display: inline-block;
	float: left;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section h2 {
	font-size: 1rem;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .4rem 0;
	width: 100%;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section > a,
.cut-nav .dropdown-section > a:visited {
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: bold;
	padding: 1rem 0;
	width: 100%;
}

/* first two */

.cut-nav .dropdown-section > a:first-of-type {
	padding-top: 1.2rem;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section .login {
	background-color: transparent;
	border: 0 none;
	color: #ccc;
	float: left;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: bold;
	padding: 0 0 2.2rem;
	text-align: left;
	width: 100%;
}

.cut-nav .dropdown-section .follow {
	background-color: #ededeb;
	border-radius: .5rem;
	border-top: 1px solid #3e3e3e;
	float: left;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .3rem 1rem;
	text-align: left;
	width: 100%;
}

.cut-nav .promoCallOut {
	display: none;
}

.embed.video {
	height: 21rem;
}

.embed.video svg {
	top: 36%;
}

/* Basics */

.img {
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	line-height: 1.3rem;
	margin: 1.6rem 0;
	position: relative;
	width: 100%;
}

.img div {
	position: relative;
}

.img img {
	width: 100%;
}

.img aside {
	bottom: 0;
	position: relative;
	right: 0;
}

.img figcaption {
	margin: .5rem 0 0;
	width: 100%;
	text-align: left;
}

.img figcaption,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] a {
	color: #353535;
}

.img figcaption .buffer {
	margin-right: .2rem;
}

.img cite {
	font-style: normal;
}

.img cite,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] cite a {
	color: #888;
}

.img .close {
	display: none;
}

/* Display Variations */

/* Thumb */

.img.thumb {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 21.5rem;
}

.img.thumb cite {
	display: inline;
}

.img.thumb aside {
	display: none;
}

/* Square */

.img.square {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 21.5rem;
}

.img.square cite {
	display: inline;
}

/* Vertical */

.img.vertical-small {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 27.6rem;
}

.img.vertical-small cite {
	margin: 0;
}

/* Large Vertical */

.img.vertical {
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
}

/* Horizontal */

.img.horizontal {
	clear: both;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
}

.img.horizontal figcaption {
	text-align: left;
	width: calc(100% - 8rem);
}

/* Secondary Image Alignment */

.img.right {
	float: right;
	margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.left {
	float: left;
	text-align: right;
	margin: 1rem 2.5rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.center {
	margin: 1.6rem 0 2.4rem;
}

/* secondary centered images shouldn't have text wrap around them */

.img.center.secondary {
	width: 100%;
	margin: 1.6rem auto 2.4rem;
	max-width: 100%;
}

.img.center.secondary img {
	margin: 0 auto;
}

/* Enlarge */

.img .enlarge {
	background-color: rgba(255,255,255, .85);
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	border-radius: .3rem;
	display: none;
	float: right;
	height: 3.2rem;
	line-height: 0;
	margin: 0 0 .6rem 1rem;
	padding: .4rem;
	text-align: center;
	width: 3.2rem;
}

.img .enlarge svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	left: .1rem;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.8rem;
}

/* Enlarged Image */

.img.enlarged {
	display: block;
	height: 100%;
	margin: 0 auto;
	max-width: none;
	position: absolute;
	text-align: center;
	width: 100%;
	z-index: 1001;
}

.img.enlarged aside {
	bottom: .7rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: .4rem;
}

.img.enlarged .enlarge {
	display: none;
}

.img.enlarged .close {
	background: none;
	border: 1px solid #3b3b3b;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: block;
	height: 3.6rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: .5rem;
	top: .5rem;
	transition: border-color .25s ease-in;
	width: 3.6rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg {
	height: 1.6rem;
	left: 0;
	margin: .9rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.6rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg path {
	fill: #fff;
}

/* Pinterest and fb */

.img aside a.fb,
.img aside a.pinterest {
	display: block;
	float: right;
	line-height: 0;
	padding: .6rem 0 0 1rem;
}

.img aside a.fb,
.img aside a.pinterest {
	border-bottom-right-radius: .3rem;
	border-left: 0;
	border-top-right-radius: .3rem;
}

.img.enlarged aside a.fb,
.img.enlarged aside a.pinterest {
	opacity: 1;
}

.img aside a.fb svg,
.img aside a.pinterest svg {
	height: 2.5rem;
	width: 2.5rem;
}

/* Slideshow button on top of primary image. */

.img.slideshow-link > div > a {
	bottom: 0;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	top: 0;
	z-index: 10;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a button {
	background-color: #000;
	border: 0;
	bottom: 1.8rem;
	color: #fff;
	display: block;
	font-family: "MillerHeadlineLight", Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	font-weight: 300;
	letter-spacing: .1rem;
	font-style: italic;
	padding: .3rem 2.7rem 1.3rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: 1.5rem;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	transition: background-color 0.2s;
	-webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a:hover button {
	background-color: #381AB1;
	cursor: pointer;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a svg {
	display: inline-block;
	height: 2.5rem;
	margin: 0 .5rem;
	position: relative;
	top: .7rem;
	width: 2.5rem;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for large vertical. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical > div > a button {
	bottom: auto;
	letter-spacing: 0;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .3rem 1.2rem 1.4rem 1.9rem;
	top: 1.5rem;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for vertical-small. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical-small > div > a button {
	bottom: 1.5rem;
	left: 1.2rem;
	padding: .3rem 0 1.3rem 1rem;
	right: 1.2rem;
	width: calc(100% - 2.4rem);
}

.package-nav {

.package-nav:after {

}

.package-nav .tags-slider-inner {

.package-nav .title,

.package-nav .item-box-link {

.related-side {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	float: left;
	margin: .8rem 2.5rem 1.5rem 0;
	padding: 2rem 1.5rem 1rem;
	position: relative;
	width: 27rem;
}

.related-side h2,
.story .body .related-side h2 {
	background-color: #fff;
	color: #555;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.3rem;
	font-style: italic;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 0;
	margin: 0;
	padding-right: .8rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: -1.2rem;
}

.related-side a,
.story .body .related-side a {
	background-position: 0 1rem;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: 5.6rem auto;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
	color: #2881B3;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	line-height: 1.3;
	min-height: 7.6rem;
	padding: 1rem 0;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.related-side a.has-image,
.story .body .related-side a.has-image {
	padding: 1rem 0 1rem 6.6rem;
}

.related-side a:hover,
.story .body .related-side a:hover {
	text-decoration: underline;
}

.related-side a:last-child,
.story .body .related-side a:last-child {
	border-bottom: 0;
}

/* container */

.share {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	display: block;
	margin: 0 0 2.5rem;
	padding: .7rem 0;
	width: 100%;
}

/* title */

.share .share-text {
	display: none;
}

/* clearfix */

.share::after {
	clear: both;
	content: '';
	display: block;
}

/* total share count */

.share .share-counter {
	display: none;
}

/* share link */

.share a {
	border-right: 1px solid #dadada;
	color: #555;
	float: left;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
	height: 2.1rem;
	margin: 0 1rem 0 0;
	padding: .4rem 0 0 3.1rem;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	width: 7.9rem;
}

/* Prevent orphan wrapping. */

.share a:last-of-type,
.share.horizontal a:last-of-type {
	border-right: none;
	width: 3rem;
}

/* count */

.share a em {
	display: none;
}

.share a.comments {
	display: none;
}

/* Icons */

.share a svg {
	height: 2.1rem;
	left: .3rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	width: 2.1rem;
}

.share a:first-of-type {
	padding-left: 3rem;
	width: 8rem;
}

.share a:first-of-type svg {
	left: 0;
	top: 0;
}

.share a.email svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	top: .3rem;
	width: 1.8rem;
}

.share a.print svg {
	height: 2.4rem;
	left: -.1rem;
	top: -.1rem;
	width: 2.4rem;
}

.share a.print span {
	display: none;
}

.share .close {
	display: none;
}

/* hide the mobile overlay (edge case) */

.share.overlay {
	display: none;
}

/* hide whatsapp (except on ios) */

.share .whatsapp {
	display: none;
}

.share .whatsapp.displayed {
	display: block;
}

.share-feed div.share-count,
.greatest-hits .share-feed div.share-count,
.most-popular .share-feed div.share-count,
.newsfeed .share-feed div.share-count {
	color: #f85d00;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: 700;
	height: auto;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
	line-height: 1;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
}

.share-feed .share-count em,
.greatest-hits .share-feed .share-count em,
.most-popular .share-feed .share-count em,
.newsfeed .share-feed .share-count em {

	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: 400;
}

.share-feed.no-count .share-count,
.newsfeed .share-feed .share-count {

}

.share-feed a.fb,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a.fb,

.newsfeed .share-feed a.fb {

.share-feed a.twit,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a.twit,
.most-popular .share-feed a.twit,
.newsfeed .share-feed a.twit {
	background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/twitter.svg);
}

.share-feed a,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a,
.most-popular .share-feed a,
.newsfeed .share-feed a {
	display: none;
}

.share-feed.no-count a,
.newsfeed .share-feed a {
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: 1.4rem 1.4rem;
	border-bottom: none;
	border-top: none;
	color: #555;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	padding: .1rem 0 .1rem 1.8rem;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.share-feed a:nth-of-type(1),
.greatest-hits .share-feed a:nth-of-type(1),
.most-popular .share-feed a:nth-of-type(1),
.newsfeed .share-feed a:nth-of-type(1) {
	border-right: 1px solid #dadada;
	border-top: none;
	margin-right: .8rem;
	padding: .1rem .8rem .1rem 1.8rem;
}

/* Article Header */

.story {
	padding-bottom: 1rem;
	position: relative;
	word-wrap: break-word;
}

.story header {
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.story header nav {
	border-bottom: 1px dotted #ccc;
	clear: both;

	height: 2.5rem;
	margin: 0 0 1rem;
	padding: 0 0 3rem;

.story.sponsored header nav {
	padding: 0 0 4rem;

.story header nav a,
.story header nav span {
	color: #111;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-weight: bold;

/* submenu fadein animation */

.cut-nav .main-submenu {
	background-color: #000;

	left: 1.5rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 75%;

}

.cut-nav .main-submenu:after,
.cut-nav .main-submenu:before {
	border: solid transparent;
	bottom: 100%;
	content: ' ';
	height: 0;
	left: 63.2%;
	pointer-events: none;
	position: absolute;
	width: 0;
}

.cut-nav .main-submenu:after {
	border-bottom-color: #000;
	border-width: 10px;
	margin-left: -10px;
}

.cut-nav .main-submenu:before {
	border-bottom-color: #4f4f4f;
	border-width: 11px;
	margin-left: -11px;
}

.cut-nav .main-submenu-item {
	-webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased;
	border-top: 1px solid #4f4f4f;
	clear: left;
	display: inline-block;
	float: left;
	font-family: MillerHeadlineLight, Georgia, serif;

	font-style: italic;
	font-weight: 300;

.cut-nav .main-submenu-item:first-of-type {

}

.cut-nav .colorful-sections a.main-submenu-item:hover {

}

/* open the submenu when fashions is hovered */

.cut-nav .main-item.fashions:hover .main-submenu {

	        animation: 200ms CutNavFadeIn forwards;

}

.cut-nav .search {

.cut-nav .search .search-icon {

.cut-nav .search-icon svg {

.cut-nav .searchtext {

/* Basics */

.img {
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	line-height: 1.3rem;
	margin: 1.6rem 0;
	position: relative;
	max-width: 100%;
}

.img div {
	position: relative;
}

.img img {
	width: 100%;
	transition: opacity .4s ease-in;
}

.img aside {
	left: .5rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: .5rem;
	transition: opacity .25s ease-in;
}

.img figcaption {
	margin: .5rem 0 0;
	width: 100%;
	text-align: left;
}

.img figcaption,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] a {
	color: #353535;
}

.img figcaption .buffer {
	margin-right: .2rem;
}

.img cite {
	font-style: normal;
}

.img cite,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] cite a {
	color: #888;
}

.img .close {
	display: none;
}

/* Display Variations */

/* Thumb */

.img.thumb {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 18.8rem;
	min-width: 14.6rem;
}

.img.thumb cite {
	display: inline;
}

.img.thumb aside {
	display: none;
}

/* Square */

.img.square {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	width: 18.8rem;
}

.img.square cite {
	display: inline;
}

/* Vertical */

.img.vertical-small {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	width: 24rem;
}

.img.vertical-small cite {
	margin: 0;
}

/* Vertical List */

.img.vertical-list figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

/* Large Vertical */

.img.vertical {
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
}

.img.vertical figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

/* Horizontal */

.img.horizontal {
	clear: both;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
	width: 52.9rem;
}

.img.horizontal figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

.img.horizontal img {
	width: 100%;
}

/* Secondary Image Alignment */

.img.right {
	float: right;
	margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.left {
	float: left;
	text-align: left;
	margin: 1rem 2.5rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.left.secondary figcaption {
	text-align: left;
}

.img.center {
	margin: 1.6rem 0 2.4rem;
	text-align: center;
}

/* secondary centered images shouldn't have text wrap around them */

.img.center.secondary {
	width: 100%;
	margin: 1.6rem auto 2.4rem;
	max-width: 100%;
}

.img.center.secondary figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

.img.center.secondary img {
	margin: 0 auto;
	width: 100%;
}

/* Enlarge Button */

.img .enlarge {
	background-color: #fff;
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	border-radius: .3rem;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: block;
	height: 3.1rem;
	line-height: 0;
	margin: 0 0 .6rem;
	opacity: .6;
	padding: .4rem;
	text-align: center;
	transition: opacity .15s ease-in;
	width: 3.1rem;
}

.img:hover .enlarge {
	opacity: 1;
}

.img .enlarge svg {
	height: 1.6rem;
	left: 0;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.6rem;
}

/* Enlarged Image */

.img.enlarged {
	-webkit-align-items: center;
	    -ms-flex-align: center;
	        align-items: center;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: -webkit-flex;
	display: -ms-flexbox;
	display: flex;
	height: 100vh;
	-webkit-justify-content: center;
	    -ms-flex-pack: center;
	        justify-content: center;
	margin: 0;
	max-width: none;
	width: 100%;
	z-index: 9999999;
}

.img.enlarged div {
	max-height: 90%; /* Read by JavaScript. Must be %. */
	max-width: 102.4rem; /* Read by JavaScript. Must be rem. */
	position: relative;
}

.img.enlarged img {
	-webkit-flex: 1 100%;
	    -ms-flex: 1 100%;
	        flex: 1 100%;
	height: auto;
	max-height: 100%;
	max-width: 100%;
	opacity: 1;
	-webkit-order: 1;
	    -ms-flex-order: 1;
	        order: 1;
	width: auto;
}

.img.enlarged .enlarge {
	display: none;
}

.img.enlarged figcaption {
	color: #fff;
	-webkit-flex: 1 100%;
	    -ms-flex: 1 100%;
	        flex: 1 100%;
	-webkit-order: 2;
	    -ms-flex-order: 2;
	        order: 2;
}

.img.enlarged figcaption cite {
	color: #fff;
}

.img.enlarged .close {
	background-color: rgba(87, 87, 87, .2);
	border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, .1);
	border-radius: .3rem;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: inline-block;
	height: 3.1rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: .5rem;
	top: .5rem;
	transition: border-color .25s ease-in;
	width: 3.1rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg {
	height: 1.6rem;
	left: 0;
	margin: .7rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.6rem;
}

.img.enlarged .close svg path {
	fill: #fff;
}

/* Pinterest and fb */

.img aside a.fb,
.img aside a.pinterest {
	background-color: rgba(255,255,255, 0.8);
	border: 1px solid #ccc;
	cursor: pointer;
	display: block;
	line-height: 0;
	margin: 0 0 .6rem;
	opacity: 0;
	padding: .3rem;
	text-align: center;
	transition: opacity .25s ease-in, background-color .15s ease-in;
}

.img aside a.pinterest {
	border-bottom: 0;
	border-top-left-radius: .3rem;
	border-top-right-radius: .3rem;
	margin-bottom: 0;
}

.img aside a.fb {
	border-bottom-left-radius: .3rem;
	border-bottom-right-radius: .3rem;
	border-top: 0;
}

.img:hover aside a.pinterest,
.img.enlarged aside a.pinterest,
.img:hover aside a.fb,
.img.enlarged aside a.fb {
	opacity: 1;
}

.img aside a.pinterest:hover,
.img aside a.fb:hover {
	opacity: 1;
	background-color: #fff;
}

.img aside a.pinterest svg,
.img aside a.fb svg {
	height: 2.3rem;
	width: 2.3rem;
}

/* Slideshow button on top of primary image. */

.img.slideshow-link > div > a {
	bottom: 0;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	top: 0;
	z-index: 10;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a button {
	background-color: #000;
	border: 1px solid #000;
	bottom: 1.8rem;
	color: #fff;
	display: block;
	font-family: "MillerHeadlineLight", Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.45rem;
	font-weight: 300;
	letter-spacing: .1rem;
	font-style: italic;
	padding: .3rem 1.2rem 1.3rem 1.9rem;
	position: absolute;
	right: 1.5rem;
	text-transform: uppercase;
	transition: background-color 0.2s;
	-webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a:hover button {
	background-color: #381AB1;
	cursor: pointer;
}

.img.slideshow-link > div > a svg {
	display: inline-block;
	height: 2.5rem;
	margin: 0 .6rem;
	position: relative;
	top: .6rem;
	width: 2.5rem;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for large vertical. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical > div > a button {
	bottom: auto;
	letter-spacing: 0;
	margin: 0;
	top: 1.5rem;
}

/* Alternate slideshow button for vertical-small. */

.img.slideshow-link.vertical-small > div > a button {
	bottom: .9rem;
	left: .9rem;
	right: .9rem;
	width: calc(100% - 1.8rem);
}

.most-popular article:nth-of-type(7) a:before {

.most-popular article:nth-of-type(8) a:before {

.package-nav {
	background-color: white;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
	height: 8rem;
	margin: 0 auto;
	max-width: 102.4rem;
	overflow: hidden;
	position: relative;
	width: 100%;
}

.stick {
	box-shadow: 0 5px 8px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, .35);
	left: 50%;
	position: fixed;
	top: 0;
	-webkit-transform: translate(-50%, 0);
	        transform: translate(-50%, 0);
	z-index: 10;
}

/* clearfix */

.package-nav:before,
.package-nav:after {
	content: '';
	display: table;
}

.package-nav:after {
	clear: both;
}

.package-nav .tags-slider-inner {
	float: left;
	height: 8rem;
	position: relative;
	width: 100%;
}

/*
.package-nav .title {
  background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/beauty-awards.png);
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-size: 95%;
  height: 100%;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  line-height: 1.9rem;
  margin: .8rem 0 0 1rem;
  width: 10.4rem;
}
*/

.package-nav .title,
.package-nav .subtitle {
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.5rem;
	font-style: italic;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.package-nav .title {
	color: #111;
	display: block;
	margin: 1.5rem 0 0 2rem;
	width: 10rem;
}

.package-nav .subtitle {
	color: #555;
	display: block;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0;
}

.package-nav .title span {
	position: absolute;
	top: -100rem;
}

.package-nav .items-wrapper {
	height: 8rem;
	left: 12.4rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 0;
}

.package-nav .items {
	height: 8rem;
	left: 0;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
	transition: .5s margin-left;
}

.package-nav .item {
	float: left;
	height: 8rem;
	position: relative;
	width: 22rem;
}

.package-nav .item:before {
	border-left: 1px solid #ededed;
	content: '';
	height: 7rem;
	left: -.5rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: 1rem;
	width: 1px;
}

.package-nav .item:first-of-type:before {
	border-left: none;
}

.package-nav .item-box-link {
	display: block;
	height: 100%;
	left: 0;
	padding: 1rem 1.4rem 0;
	position: absolute;
	text-decoration: none;
	top: 0;
	width: 100%;
}

.package-nav .item-image {
	background-position: center bottom;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: contain;
	bottom: 1rem;
	height: 6rem;
	left: .5rem;
	position: absolute;
	width: 6rem;
}

.package-nav .item-title,
.package-nav .item-link {
	float: left;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	padding: 0;
}

.package-nav .item-title {
	color: #171717;
	font-size: 1.3rem;
	line-height: 1.2;
	margin: .4rem 0 0 5.9rem;
	width: 67%;
}

.package-nav .item-link {
	color: #5f5f5f;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	margin: .25rem 0 0 5.3rem;
	transition: color 350ms ease-out, border 350ms ease-out;
}

.package-nav .item-title:hover {
	color: #1782a9;
}

.package-nav .items-wrapper {
	overflow-x: hidden;
	overflow-y: hidden;
	width: calc(100% - 22.4rem) !important; /* this is set dynamically in markup for smaller viewports */
}

/* prev/next buttons */

.package-nav .buttons {
	display: block;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	top: .8rem;
	width: 10rem;
}

.package-nav .buttons:before {
	border-left: 1px solid #ededed;
	content: '';
	height: 6rem;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
	top: 10.5rem;
	width: 1px;
}

.package-nav .prev,
.package-nav .next {
	background: #f5f5f5;
	border: 1px solid #d1d1d1;
	border-radius: 3px;
	cursor: pointer;
	float: left;
	height: 6.4rem;
	padding: 2rem 1.3rem;
	position: relative;
	transition: background 350ms ease-out, border 350ms ease-out;
	width: 4rem;
}

.package-nav .prev svg,
.package-nav .next svg {
	fill: #000 !important;
	height: 2.2rem;
	width: 1.2rem;
}

.package-nav .prev:hover,
.package-nav .next:hover {
	background: #ffe400;
	border: 1px solid #f1d803;
	transition: background 200ms ease-out, border 200ms ease-out;
}

.package-nav.is-beginning .prev,
.package-nav.is-end .next {
	background: #fcfcfc !important;
	border: 1px solid #f1f1f1 !important;
	cursor: default;
}

.package-nav.is-beginning .prev svg,
.package-nav.is-end .next svg {
	fill: #d7d7d7 !important;
}

.package-nav .next {
	margin-left: 1rem;
}

.package-nav .next svg {
	-webkit-transform: rotate(180deg);
	        transform: rotate(180deg);
}

.related-side {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	float: left;
	margin: .8rem 2.5rem 1.5rem 0;
	padding: .5rem 0 0;
	position: relative;
	width: 19rem;
}

.related-side h2,
.story .body .related-side h2 {
	background-color: #fff;
	color: #555;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: italic;
	font-weight: bold;
	margin: 0;
	padding-right: .8rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: -1.2rem;
}

.related-side a,
.story .body .related-side a {
	background-position: 0 1rem;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: 4.7rem auto;
	border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1;
	color: #2881b3;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-weight: 700;
	line-height: 1.2;
	min-height: 6.7rem;
	padding: 1rem 0;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.related-side a.has-image,
.story .body .related-side a.has-image {
	padding: 1rem 0 1rem 5.7rem;
}

.related-side a:last-child,
.story .body .related-side a:last-child {
	border-bottom: 0;
}

/* container */

.share {
	border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
	display: block;
	margin: 0 0 4.5rem 0;
	padding: 1.4rem 0 0;
	width: 11rem;
}

.share em {
	font-style: normal;
}

/* title */

.share .share-text {
	display: none;
}

/* total share count */

.share .share-counter {
	color: #f6a303;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
	margin: 0 0 1.7rem;
	padding: 0 .6rem;
}

.share .share-counter em {
	color: #000;
	display: block;
	font-size: 1.3rem;
}

/* share link */

.share a {
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	color: #555;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
	height: 2.6rem;
	margin: 0 0 .9rem;
	padding: 1.1rem 0 0 2.9rem;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	width: 10.9rem;
}

/* share icons */

.share a svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	position: absolute;
	left: .5rem;
	top: .7rem;
	width: 1.8rem;
}

.share a.email svg {
	height: 1.7rem;
	left: .6rem;
	top: 1rem;
	width: 1.7rem;
}

.share a.comments svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	left: .5rem;
	top: .8rem;
	width: 1.7rem;
}

.share a.print svg {
	height: 2.2rem;
	left: .3rem;
	top: .6rem;
	width: 2.2rem;
}

/* count */

.share a em {
	border-left: 1px solid #dadada;
	bottom: 0;
	color: #000;
	display: block;
	font-weight: bold;
	margin-top: 1rem;
	padding: 0;
	position: absolute;
	right: 0;
	text-align: center;
	top: 0;
	width: 3.4em;
}

/* specific share tools */

.share a.comments {
	color: #000;
	font-weight: bold;
}

.share a.email {
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	font-weight: normal;
}

.share a.print {
	font-weight: normal;
	margin: -.2rem 0 0;
}

.share .close {
	display: none;
}

/* horizontal (direction set in json) */

.share.horizontal {
	border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
	padding: 1rem 0;
	margin-bottom: 3rem;
	width: 100%;
}

.share.horizontal::after {
	clear: both;
	content: '';
	display: block;
}

.share.horizontal .share-counter {
	display: none;
}

.share.horizontal a {
	background-position: 0;
	border-right: 1px solid #dadada;
	border-top: none;
	float: left;
	height: 1.8rem;
	margin: 0 1rem 0 0;
	padding: .4rem 0 0 2.4rem;
	width: 6.5rem;
}

.share.horizontal a:last-of-type {
	border-right: none;
}

.share.horizontal a em {
	display: none;
}

/* share icons */

.share.horizontal a svg {
	height: 1.8rem;
	position: absolute;
	left: 0;
	top: 0;
	width: 1.8rem;
}

.share.horizontal a.email svg {
	height: 1.7rem;
	top: .3rem;
	width: 1.7rem;
}

.share.horizontal a.print svg {
	height: 2.2rem;
	top: -.1rem;
	width: 2.2rem;
}

.share.horizontal a.print span {
	display: none;
}

/* hide the mobile overlay (edge case) */

.share.overlay {
	display: none;
}

/* hide whatsapp (except on ios) */

.share .whatsapp {
	display: none;
}

.share .whatsapp.displayed {
	display: block;
}

.share-feed,
.greatest-hits .share-feed,
.most-popular .share-feed,
.newsfeed .share-feed {
	height: 1.6rem;
	overflow: hidden;
}

.share-feed div.share-count,
.greatest-hits section.share-feed div.share-count,
.most-popular section.share-feed div.share-count,
.newsfeed section.share-feed div.share-count,
.top-stories section.share-feed div.share-count {
	color: #f85d00;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: 700;
	height: 1.6rem;
	left: 0;
	line-height: 1;
	margin: 0;
	padding: 0 0 .1rem;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
}

.share-feed  .share-count em,
.greatest-hits .share-feed .share-count em,
.most-popular .share-feed .share-count em,
.newsfeed .share-feed .share-count em {
	color: #555;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: 400;
}

.share-feed a,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a,
.most-popular .share-feed a,
.newsfeed .share-feed a {
	background-position: 0;
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: 1.4rem 1.4rem;
	border-bottom: none;
	border-top: none;
	color: #555;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-weight: 400;
	opacity: .2;
	padding: .1rem 0 .1rem 1.8rem;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.share-feed a.fb,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a.fb,
.most-popular .share-feed a.fb,
.newsfeed .share-feed a.fb {
	background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/facebook.svg);
}

.share-feed a.twit,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a.twit,
.most-popular .share-feed a.twit,
.newsfeed .share-feed a.twit {
	background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/twitter.svg);
}

.share-feed a:hover,
.greatest-hits .share-feed a:hover,
.most-popular .share-feed a:hover,
.newsfeed .share-feed a:hover {
	text-decoration: none;
}

.share-feed a:nth-of-type(1),
.most-popular .share-feed a:nth-of-type(1),
.newsfeed .share-feed a:nth-of-type(1) {
	border-right: 1px solid #dadada;
	margin-right: .8rem;
	padding: .1rem .8rem .1rem 1.8rem;
}

section.share-feed a.fb:before,
article:hover .share-feed div.share-count,
.top-stories div div:hover .share-feed div.share-count,
.most-popular article:hover .share-feed div.share-count {
	display: none;
}

article:hover .share-feed a,
.greatest-hits article:hover .share-feed a,
.top-stories div div:hover .share-feed a,
.most-popular article:hover .share-feed a {
	color: #000;
	display: inline-block;
	opacity: 1;
	transition: opacity .8s;
}

/* Components that hide count. */

.share-feed.no-count div.share-count,
a:hover .share-feed.no-count div.share-count,
article:hover .share-feed.no-count div.share-count,
.scienceofus .newsfeed .share-feed div.share-count,
.scienceofus .newsfeed a:hover .share-feed div.share-count,
.scienceofus .newsfeed article:hover .share-feed div.share-count,
.grubstreet .newsfeed .share-feed div.share-count,
.grubstreet .newsfeed a:hover .share-feed div.share-count,
.grubstreet .newsfeed article:hover .share-feed div.share-count {
	display: none;
}

/* Article Header */

.story {
	padding-bottom: 2rem;
	position: relative;
	word-wrap: break-word;
}

/* manual clearfix */

.story:before,
.story:after {
	content: '';
	display: table;
}

.story:after {
	clear: both;
}

.story header {
	display: block;
	margin-bottom: 2rem;
	position: relative;
}

.story header nav {
	clear: both;
	display: block;
	height: 2.5rem;
	margin: 0 0 1rem;
}

.story header nav a,
.story header nav span {
	color: #111;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	height: 2rem;
	line-height: 2.4rem;
	padding-left: 1.8rem;
	text-decoration: none;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.story header nav a.rubric::before,
.story header nav span:last-child::before {
	content: '/';
	color: #999;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	position: relative;
	left: -.9rem;
	top: .1rem;
}

.story.sponsored header nav span:before {
	content: "";
}

.story header nav span.exclusive {
	color: #00bcf1;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	text-transform: capitalize;
}

.story header nav span.breaking {
	color: #ec2c00;
	font-size: 1.25rem;
	text-transform: capitalize;
}

.story.sponsored header nav span.sponsored-tag,
.story.sponsored header nav span.sponsored-tag:last-child {
	background-color: #ff003d;
	border-radius: .2rem;
	color: #fff;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 1.2rem;
	padding: .25rem .5rem;
	text-transform: none;
}

.story .di-logo {
	background-image: url(//cache.nymag.com/media/di-logo.2x.png);
	background-size: 8.2rem 2rem;
	color: transparent;
	display: block;
	float: left;
	padding-right: .5rem;
	height: 2rem;
	width: 8.2rem;
}

.story header h1 {
	color: #323232;
	font-family: GeorgiaProCondSemiBold, serif;
	font-size: 2.7rem;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 2.7rem;
	margin: 0 0 1.3rem;
}

.story.sponsored header h1 {
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: bold;
}

.story header p {
	color: #333;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.7rem;
	line-height: 1.3rem;
}

/* Byline */

.story header .by-authors {
	color: #333;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author {
	color: #333;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 0;
	position: relative;
	text-decoration: none;
	transition: color .25s;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author:first-child {
	padding-left: 0;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author:hover {
	color: #08C;
}

.story header .by-authors iframe {
	position: relative;
	top: .4rem;
	margin-left: 1rem;
}

/* Author Avatar */

.story header .by-authors .story-author-img {
	background-repeat: no-repeat;
	background-size: contain;
	border-radius: 5rem;
	display: inline-block;
	height: 5rem;
	margin: 0 .5rem 0 0;
	vertical-align: middle;
	width: 5rem;
}

/* Stacked format - img + name + twitter */

.story header .by-authors.stacked {
	margin-bottom: -3rem;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked,
.story header .by-authors.stacked .story-author {
	display: block;
	margin-top: 2rem;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .story-author-img {
	position: relative;
	top: -1rem;
	vertical-align: top;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .by {
	font-weight: normal;
}

.story header .by-authors a.story-author:hover .by {
	color: #000;
	cursor: text;
}

.story header .by-authors.stacked .twitter {
	left: 4rem;
	position: relative;
	top: -3rem;
}

/* Time */

.story header time {
	bottom: -5.5rem;
	color: #555;
	display: block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	left: -13rem;
	line-height: 1.6rem;
	position: absolute;
}

.story header time span {
	display: block;
}

.story header .share {
	bottom: -41.6rem;
	left: -13.4rem;
	margin: 0;
	min-height: 34rem;
	position: absolute;
}

/* Article Body */

.story .body {
	color: #111;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.6rem;
	padding-right: 1rem;
}

/* Secondary Images */

.story .body .image.right,
.story .body figure.right {
	float: right;
	margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.story .body .image.left,
.story .body figure.left {
	float: left;
	text-align: left;
	margin: 1rem 2.5rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.story .body .image.center,
.story .body figure.center {
	margin: 1.6rem 0 2.4rem;
	text-align: center;
}

/* Slideshow button at the end of the article. */

.story .body a.begin-slideshow {
	background-color: #000;
	border: 1px solid #222;
	bottom: 1.7rem;
	clear: both;
	color: #fff;
	display: block;
	font-family: "MillerHeadlineLight", Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.8rem;
	font-style: italic;
	font-weight: 300;
	margin: 1.75em 0;
	padding: 1.2rem 1.9rem 1.2rem;
	text-align: center;
	transition: background .2s, border .2s, color .2s;
	-webkit-font-smoothing: subpixel-antialiased;
}

.story .body a.begin-slideshow:hover {
	background: #381AB1;
	border: 1px solid #444;
	color: #fff;
}

.story .body .story-img figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

.story .body iframe {
	border: none;
	margin: .8rem 0 2.4rem;
	min-height: 37rem;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .twitter-tweet {
	min-height: 0;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .instagram-embed {
	height: 64.2rem;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .vine-embed {
	height: 70rem;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .soundcloud-embed {
	height: 16.6rem;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 100%;
}

.story .body .audio-embed {
	height: 5.4rem;
	min-height: 54px;
	width: 100%;
}

.story .body .video-embed {
	width: 100%;
	height: auto;
	margin: .8rem 0 2.4rem;
}

.story .body .video-embed iframe {
	margin: 0;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 100%;
}

.story .body .giphy-square {
	height: 52.8rem;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .giphy-standard {
	height: 39.6rem;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .giphy-hd {
	height: 29.7rem;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .giphy-widescreen {
	height: 22.5rem;
	min-height: 0;
	width: 52.8rem;
}

.story .body .fb-post {
	margin-bottom: 3.8rem;
}

.story .body .imgur-embed img {
	width: 100%;
}

.story .body h2 {

@media print {

* {
	background: transparent;
	box-shadow: none;
	color: #000;
	text-shadow: none;
}

html {
	background-color: #fff;
}

body {
	padding: .5in;
}

/* Article */

article {
	color: #111;
	margin: 0;
	padding: .1in .5in;
	width: 100%;
}

article p {
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	line-height: 1.9rem;
}

a[href] {
	border: none;
	color: #000;
	font-weight: bold;
	text-decoration: none;
}

a[href^="#"]:after {
	content: "";
}

abbr[title]:after {
	content: " (" attr(title) ")";
}

/* For story - Add links after */

.body a[href^=http]:after {
	color: #999;
	content: " (" attr(href) ") ";
	font-weight: normal;
}

/* For story - Add links after for //www. */

.body a[href^="//www."]:after {
	color: #999;
	content: " (http:" attr(href) ") ";
	font-weight: normal;
}

/* Hidden */

nav,
aside,
.ad {
	display: none;
}

.ad {
	display: none!important;
}

.ad-recirc {
	display: none;
}

.column-subscribe {

}

/* Hidden */

.cut-nav div > * {

}

	bottom: 0;

	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-weight: normal;
	line-height: 0;

	right: 0;
	text-align: right;

.cut-nav .cut-nav-inner {
	height: 4rem;
	padding: 0;
	background: none;
}

/* Logo */

.cut-nav .logo {
	display: inline-block;
	height: 4rem;
	left: .5%;
	margin: 0;
	position: relative;
	top: 0;
	width: 20rem;
}

.cut-nav .logo svg {
	fill: #000;
	height: 4rem;
	max-width: 100%;
	width: auto;
}

.cut-nav .logo svg * {
	fill: #000;
}

.global-nav {
	display: none;
}

/* Basics */

.img {
	cursor: pointer;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	line-height: 1.3rem;
	margin: 1.6rem 0;
	position: relative;
	max-width: 100%;
}

.img div {
	position: relative;
}

.img img {
	max-width: 100%;
	transition: opacity .4s ease-in;
}

.img aside {
	left: .5rem;
	position: absolute;
	top: .5rem;
	transition: opacity .25s ease-in;
}

.img figcaption {
	margin: .5rem 0 0;
	width: 100%;
	text-align: left;
}

.img figcaption,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] a {
	color: #353535;
}

.img figcaption .buffer {
	margin-right: .2rem;
}

.img cite {
	font-style: normal;
}

.img cite,
.img figcaption[itemprop='caption'] cite a {
	color: #888;
}

/* Display Variations */

/* Thumb */

.img.thumb {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 18.8rem;
}

.img.thumb cite {
	display: inline;
}

.img.thumb .pinterest {
	display: none;
}

/* Square */

.img.square {
	float: left;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 0;
	width: 18.8rem;
}

.img.square cite {
	display: inline;
}

/* Vertical */

.img.vertical-small {
	display: inline-block;
	margin: .5rem 2rem 1rem 1.2rem;
	max-width: 24rem;
}

.img.vertical-small cite {
	margin: 0;
}

/* Large Vertical */

.img.vertical {
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
}

.img.vertical figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

/* Horizontal */

.img.horizontal {
	clear: both;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
	max-width: 7.5in;
}

.img.horizontal figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

/* Video */

.img.video {
	clear: both;
	margin: .5rem 0 2.1rem;
}

/* Secondary Image Alignment */

.img.right {
	float: right;
	margin: 1rem 0 1rem 2.5rem;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.left {
	float: left;
	text-align: left;
	margin: 1rem 2.5rem 1rem 0;
	max-width: 25rem;
}

.img.left.secondary figcaption {
	text-align: left;
}

.img.center {
	margin: 1.6rem 0 2.4rem;
	text-align: center;
}

/* secondary centered images shouldn't have text wrap around them */

.img.center.secondary {
	width: 100%;
	margin: 1.6rem auto 2.4rem;
	max-width: 100%;
}

.img.center.secondary figcaption {
	text-align: center;
}

.img.center.secondary img {
	margin: 0 auto;
	width: 100%;
}

/* slideshow button */

.img.slideshow-link > div > a {
	display: none;
}

.img aside a.pinterest {
	display: none;
}

.img .view-slideshow-button {
	display: none;
}

.img .enlarge {
	display: none;
}

.img .close {
	display: none;
}

.interstitial {
	display: none;
}

.most-popular {
	display: none;
}

.most-popular-ab2-d {
	display: none;
}

.most-popular-ab2-e {
	display: none;
}

.most-popular-ab2-f {
	display: none;
}

.most-popular-ab2-g {
	display: none;
}

.newsletter-signup {
	display: none;
}

.package-nav {
	display: none;
}

.prev-next {
	display: none;
}

.quiz {
	display: none;
}

.related-side {
	display: none;
}

.share {
	display: none;
}

.share-feed {
	display: none;
}

.share-mini {
	display: none;
}

.share-mini-alternative1 {
	display: none;
}

.share-mini-alternative2 {
	display: none;
}

/* Hidden */

.story header nav,
.story .twitter,
.story .body a.begin-slideshow,
.story header .by-authors iframe,
.story .body iframe {
	display: none; /* hide all embeded video, etc */
}

/* Article Header */

.story header h1 {
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: .23in;
	font-weight: normal;
	margin-bottom: 1rem;
	margin-top: 1rem;
}

.story header time {
	color: #333;
	display: inline-block;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	margin-top: .15rem;
	text-decoration: none;
}

.story header time span {
	color: #333;
}

.story header .by-authors {
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1rem;
	font-style: normal;
	font-weight: normal;
}

/* Article Body */

.story .body {
	color: #111;
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.2rem;
	padding-right: 1rem;
}

.story .body h2 {
	font-size: 1.4rem;
	font-weight: bold;
	line-height: 2rem;
	margin: 3rem 0 2rem;
}

.story .body p {
	font-family: Georgia, serif;
	font-size: 1.1rem;
	line-height: 2rem;
	margin: 0 0 2rem 1.5rem;
}

.story .body ul {
	clear: both;
	padding: 0 0 0 1rem;
	position: relative;
}

.story .body ul li {
	list-style: none;
	margin: 0 0 2rem;
}

.story .body ul li:before {
	color: #999;
	content: '•';
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
}

.story .body ol {
	counter-reset: list;
	padding: 0 0 0 2rem;
	position: relative;
}

.story .body ol li {
	display: block;
	list-style: none;
	margin: 0 0 2rem;
	padding: 0;
}

.story .body ol li:before {
	color: #999;
	content: counter(list);
	counter-increment: list;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-weight: bold;
	left: 0;
	position: absolute;
}

.story .body blockquote {
	border-left: 5px solid #eee;
	clear: both;
	margin: 0;
	padding-left: 1.5rem;
}

/* Article Footer */

.story footer cite a {
	color: #888;
	font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
	font-size: 1rem;
	margin-right: 1.5rem;
	padding-right: 1.3rem;
	text-decoration: none;
	text-transform: uppercase;
}

.story footer cite a:before {
	content: 'Sources: ';
}

.subnav-slider {
	display: none;
}

.taboola {
	display: none;
}

.tags {
	display: none;
}

.top-stories-desktop {
	display: none;
}

}

<div class="ledeExcerpt">Saoirse Ronan on seeing Santa in the sky and returning to the city of her birth. </div>

<div class="ledeExtras"><span class="ledeBy">Photographs by</span> Erik Madigan Heck</div>

      </a><p><i>Eight years ago, Saoirse Ronan made her first impression on U.S. audiences in </i>Atonement<i> as Briony, the confused, vengeful girl whose lie sets the plot in motion. That watchful, unsettling performance won her an Oscar nomination at age 13. Since then, she has made a couple of film appearances per year at most (a child assassin holding her own against Cate Blanchett in </i>Hanna<i>; a clever baker in </i><a data-track="Body Text Link: Internal: vulture" href="http://www.vulture.com/2014/02/movie-review-grand-budapest-hotel.html">The Grand Budapest Hotel</a>)<i>, staying more or less above the Hollywood fray (thanks in large part to the grounding influence of her parents — her father, Paul, is a working actor). That may prove tougher now: At 21, she’s again an <a data-track="Body Text Link: Internal: vulture" href="http://www.vulture.com/2015/09/2016-oscars-best-actress-category-is-stacked.html">Oscar nominee</a>, this time as a leading actress, for her performance as Irish immigrant Eilis in </i>Brooklyn<i>. Ronan’s own immigration experience was the opposite of Eilis’s: She was born in the Bronx and lived there until she was 3, then moved back to Ireland. But now she’s returned to the city that has such a hold on her imagination to make her Broadway debut in </i>The Crucible<i> as Abigail Williams — a confused, vengeful girl not unlike her first big role. We talked to her about going onstage for the first time and discussing child stardom with Jodie Foster. Her name, by the way, is <a data-track="Body Text Link: Internal: vulture" href="http://www.vulture.com/2016/01/let-ryan-gosling-teach-you-to-pronounce-saoirse.html">pronounced </a></i>Sir-sha. —<i>Rebecca Milzoff</i><br>
</p>
<p>“We moved back to Ireland when I was 3, so only certain things stick out in my head, but the memories I have seem kind of vivid. It’s just little things, like I remember one time my mom took me to the supermarket and she bought marshmallows and beer [<i>laughs</i>]. And the supermarket was a good walk away from the apartment, and we were in the Bronx, so there were hills, and I remember she put the crate of beer on the pram that she used and then she was like, ‘Here, you sit on top.’ So I sat on top of the crate of beer! She’s a great mother, I promise. And I remember one Christmas, when, to this day, I’m convinced, I was looking out the window and I saw Santa Claus in the sky with all his reindeer. Mom and Dad have video footage of it, and my dad was at the other window out of my sight ringing these bells. Whatever kind of time I had here, it has given me a very strong connection to the city. When I came back, it instantly felt right. There are things about the city that are new that you have to get used to, but it doesn’t get me down, it really just excites me. I feel like with New York, more than anywhere else, any struggle you have, any hurdle you have to overcome, everyone else has faced exactly the same thing. It makes you feel like you’re never really alone, you know? New York is made up of every other country; there’s hardly any native New Yorkers here, really. Half of the cast in our play are Irish and English. I actually feel closer to Ireland here than I did when I lived anywhere else.</p>

<a href="http://nymag.com/thecut/2016/02/colm-toibin-on-saoirse-ronans-new-york.html" data-track="related-stories">
	<aside class="leftModule">
	  <div><img src="http://pixel.nymag.com/imgs/fashion/daily/2016/02/04/magazine/05-side-saoirse-2.jpg" /></div>
		<div><p class="sectionDescription">Related</p>
	  <h1 class="sectionHed"><em>Brooklyn</em> Author Colm Tóibín on Saoirse Ronan’s New York</h1></div>
	</aside>
</a>
<p>When you go to L.A., everyone has an idea in their head of what L.A. is or what Hollywood is, and it&rsquo;s just not like that at all &mdash; it&rsquo;s just a big desert where everything&rsquo;s spread out. I feel like you come to New York and it just exceeds your expectations. Every now and again, you just go, &lsquo;I&rsquo;m in New York. This is fuckin&rsquo; great.&rsquo; I did that the other day &mdash; I was on the subway and I thought, <i>The last time I was properly on a subway train I was 3!</i></p>
<p>I do feel like if they took a cloth to scrub them a little bit it wouldn&rsquo;t hurt [<i>laughs</i>]. Even the subway train we had in <i>Brooklyn </i>&mdash; I had no idea that&rsquo;s how it would have been 50 years ago, but Jesus, can you imagine in the summer how hot it would&rsquo;ve been?</p>
<p>I&rsquo;ve only hung out in Brooklyn a little bit, to be honest. We only did two days shooting for <i>Brooklyn</i> on Clinton Street, and I&rsquo;ve gone back there since &mdash; I have friends who live in Boerum Hill and Cobble Hill. I imagine if I were to stay here after the play, which I most likely will, that&rsquo;s where I&rsquo;d go. It&rsquo;s got such a lovely feel, doesn&rsquo;t it? Such a nice neighborhood feel.</p>
<p>I literally have never, ever, done a professional play before. I had done school plays when I was 5 to 12 &mdash; a tree, an evil queen; I think I played a bumblebee. But apart from that [no] theater at all. I was always cautious about taking on a play when I was younger. I knew from my dad&rsquo;s own experience that you really need stamina. He never went to school for it. Mom and he just came over to work &mdash; a lot of that generation chose work over college because it was kind of the more realistic route at the time. And Mom became a nanny and my dad started working in a bar. And a lot of Irish actors would go in and they got to know him, and one of them eventually asked him to audition for a play. He just learned on the job. I think it was the best way for both of us &mdash; it shaped how we work. So I was aware that to take on something like that when you were just a kid, to me it would&rsquo;ve been just a bit presumptuous. But I&rsquo;ve always said that when I was about 21, that&rsquo;s when I&rsquo;d do a play.</p>

    <figcaption itemprop="caption">
        <span>Ben Whishaw and Ronan in rehearsals for <i>The Crucible.</i></span>
        <span class="buffer"></span>
      
      
        <cite>
         
          Photo:
        
          Jan Versweyveld
        </cite>
      
    </figcaption>
</figure>
<p>I only just started rehearsals. You feel everything. Your brain just doesn&rsquo;t stop. It&rsquo;s different from film &mdash; usually my preparation is learning my lines and then going on set and trying different things out, and hopefully you capture it and then it&rsquo;s done, out of your hands. Whereas with a play, it&rsquo;s constantly evolving. There&rsquo;s no real respite. You&rsquo;re thinking of every possible [meaning] one line could have.</p>
<p>Abigail is almost like Briony if she was about 16. I think with Abigail, there&rsquo;s this sense of abandonment that all the girls have. There were so many attacks on these little Puritan villages, and so many of their parents were killed &mdash; so that sense of authority they&rsquo;d get from parents is gone. John Proctor kind of gives her that purpose and makes her feel like she&rsquo;s stronger and bigger. A lot of the [orphaned] girls back then were swapped around from one household to the next; once they got to a certain age they were sent to live with a different family. So you&rsquo;re surrounded by this fairly cold community, with rules for everything, and she&rsquo;s a teenager becoming a sexual creature but she&rsquo;s still a child in some ways &mdash; there&rsquo;s just loads to think about, and I&rsquo;m still bloody figuring it out, and I know I will be for quite a while.</p>
<p>We rehearsed a scene today where gradually everyone quietly starts to turn on each other and looks as though they could kill someone, and you see how, like in &shy;religion, it can become so extreme when you follow it to the letter. Suddenly you&rsquo;re not able to be human, almost, you know? Of course they ended up taking people to court if someone looked at them wrong, or blaming someone for the loss of their child, or whatever it is. I started reading this book by Stacy Schiff, and to know that at the time, some men got into Harvard based off, like, the amount of meat that was given by their fathers to the college! A whole round of beef would pay for a year&rsquo;s tuition. It&rsquo;s mental.</p>
<p>It&rsquo;s funny, I didn&rsquo;t really feel [some of the pressures of Hollywood] when I was younger. I feel it a bit now, and I could see a change when <i>Hanna</i> came out, because it was the first sort of commercial success I&rsquo;d had, apart from <i>Atonement,</i> and I was very young then &mdash; a lot of that went over my head. Part of it was that I&rsquo;d grown up outside L.A., so I wasn&rsquo;t exposed to the competitive side of that world, where you feel like you have to do a thousand and one things in order to keep up with everyone else. I didn&rsquo;t have that pressure of feeling like I needed to be exposed more or do a big studio film in order to get more work. It was down to the type of work I wanted to do. At the end of the day, it&rsquo;s sort of like your portfolio. A piece of work is something you put time and hard work into, and you want to be able to stand next to it and say you really believed in it. </p>

<p>I was talking to someone who started out as a child actor, last night, and went on to do incredible things, and we were both saying it was a huge, huge influence to have our mothers with us when we were young and mothers who came from more of an ethical standpoint than a business one. To have someone with you from 10 to 19 when you&rsquo;re on a set, who has perspective and is only there to look out for you, it really means that you have a more realistic way of looking at this entire world. [It was] Jodie Foster. She&rsquo;s absolutely amazing.&rdquo;</p>
